Chapter 3
Loops + if Statments
---------------------

The Chapter Game: The Guessing Game
-----------------------------------
-Computer chooses a number between 1 - #?
-The user tries to guess the number
-The computer responses by letting them know if they are "too high", "too low", "correct"

The Challenges
--------------
#1- Fortune Cookie Game
The program would randomly display one of 5 fortunes each time it is run

#2- Coin Flip Game
-The program would flip a coin 100 time
-Then tell you how many times it got Heads & Tails

#3- Guess Game (modded)
The user has only a limited number of guesses

#4 - Guessing Game Reversed
-The user chooses the number
-The computer has the guess the number


